-----------
Poslib NEWS
-----------

When I (occasionally) update this file, it will contain some release highlights.

Poslib 0.9.2
 * Full IPv6 support (was a bit incomplete and buggy before), both for servers
   and clients.
 * Support for a load more platforms
 * Yet some more bug fixes

Poslib 0.9.1
 * Added async stop for client resolver
 * Added Borland C++ support
 * Various bug fixes

Poslib 0.9.0
 * Initial release